g.text: Register the server using the uuid
SLIP encoded data: 2 Bytes address + data
Server: Assign address for this client socket (0x0001)
Any incomming and outgoing data will
be from the connected nymea instance
Connected: The client can now communicate with nymea directly.
The proxy will not interpret any data from the client, and from the server only
the transmission frame (SLIP + 2 bytes of address)
